        <p>A kind of extended monastic history of Ethiopia in the version of
          <placeName ref="INS0341DL">the monastery Dabra Libānos</placeName>
          developed from the monastic genealogy of <persName ref="PRS9162TaklaHa">St Takla Hāymānot</persName>,
          that shows his spiritual descendance from <persName ref="PRS1962Anthony">St Anthony</persName>. Partly
           based on <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3973GadlaT">the Vita of Takla Hāymānot</ref>.
         </p>
